caption:
Happy Birthday to the iconic, suave Billy Dee Williams! ✨⁠
⁠
A legend who redefined what it meant to be a romantic lead in Hollywood. As one of the first brown-skinned matinee idols, he opened doors, changed perceptions, and brought undeniable style and swagger to the big screen.⁠
⁠
From “Lady Sings the Blues” to “Star Wars,” his legacy is everlasting. Happy early birthday to a true icon! 🖤⁠
